{
  "stem": "10.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 66.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is the general Zionist youth organization on the more religious side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you might enjoy it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to see him in the evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I met other people there-- the members and the board of directors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I went another night and another night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I started to join it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in no time after a couple of weeks, they put me already on the board of directors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in a few months, I became the leader of the organization in Katowice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had branches naturally all over Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in our state of Silesia, there were branches too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it became the leader of the state.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The activities differed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had meetings about history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had like, for instance, I became in charge of the Keren Kayemet, of the national fund-- Israel National Fund.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was elected to the Zionist organization as a delegate to the congress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And those were my activities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the summer, we arranged summer camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "First, I arranged the summer camp for our state only.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was in charge of the camp-- about 400, 500 young boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we spent four weeks in the mountains in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After this camp in July, in August, we had the camp for all Poland, for all members in Poland in the mountains, in the Tatra Mountains.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was on the Polish-Czechoslovakian border high up in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is part of the Carpathian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there, there were mostly leaders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we spent there four weeks too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In '39, it was about the end of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the last few days, we formed groups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went for hikes in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was supposed to be one of the leaders of the groups.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I told them, listen, I cannot go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I have to go back to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My vacation is through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I have to be back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And somebody else took over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when I returned home, in the morning, I got up in order to go to the pharmacy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I turned on the radio when I heard a terrible accident in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They ran in bad weather in thunder and lightning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the leader of the group which I was supposed to lead got killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And many were hurt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't go back to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I went to the next train back to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I helped in the rescues naturally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But even in the camps, I was always in care of the ambulance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I was a doctor in the camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There were sick people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then if somebody was really serious sick, I took him down to the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the doctor took over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And this was the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "In that time, I was engaged to a girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we decided naturally to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I sent her in '39 in April to Palestine in order that I would be soon following.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But I couldn't do it because I was in charge of the illegal Aliyah, of the illegal immigration from Poland to enter Palestine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And my friends said, Sig, you have time, you can always go because my papers were ready.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But I stayed another month and other months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And it came September 1, when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we were right on the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "The Germans entered in the morning, September 1, crossed the border without declaring war and started to enter Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But the night before, they bombarded all Polish airports.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
